---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';

const updated = "October 3, 2025";
---

<Layout title="About Knit by Machine" description="Learn about Sue Jalowiec and the mission behind Knit by Machine - 15 years helping knitters like you.">
  <style>
    :root {
      --kbm-green: #52682d;
      --kbm-green-2: #738c52;
      --page-bg: #f7f8f7;
    }

    main {
      max-width: 1100px;
      padding: 80px 20px;
      margin: 0 auto;
    }

    h1 {
      font-size: clamp(1.8rem, 3.5vw, 2.4rem);
      margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
    }

    h2 {
      font-size: 1.4rem;
      margin-top: 2rem;
    }

    p {
      margin: 1rem 0;
    }

    .subhead {
      color: var(--kbm-green);
      font-weight: 600;
      margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    }

    /* ===== Responsive Banner / Placeholder ===== */
    .banner {
      position: relative;
      width: 100%;
      border-radius: 16px;
      overflow: hidden;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--kbm-green), var(--kbm-green-2));
      color: #fff;
      box-shadow: 0 4px 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.15);
      margin-bottom: 2rem;

      /* desktop height */
      min-height: 260px;

      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      text-align: center;
      padding: 2rem;
    }

    /* inner text wrapper so we can style headline/text later next to an image */
    .banner-content {
      max-width: 600px;
    }

    .banner-title {
      font-size: clamp(1.4rem, 1vw, 1.6rem);
      font-weight: 600;
      line-height: 1.3;
      letter-spacing: 0.4px;
      margin: 0 0 .5rem 0;
    }

    .banner-note {
      font-size: .95rem;
      line-height: 1.4;
      opacity: 0.9;
      margin: 0;
    }

    /* space reserved for future headshot / product image */
    .banner-photo {
      position: absolute;
      right: 1.5rem;
      bottom: 1.5rem;
      width: 96px;
      height: 96px;
      border-radius: 12px;
      background: rgba(255,255,255,0.15);
      border: 2px solid rgba(255,255,255,0.5);
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      font-size: .8rem;
      font-weight: 600;
      text-align: center;
      line-height: 1.2;
    }

    /* On smaller screens: shorter banner, photo drops below text so it doesn't overlap */
    @media (max-width: 640px) {
      .banner {
        min-height: 180px;
        padding: 1.5rem;
      }

      .banner-photo {
        position: static;
        width: 80px;
        height: 80px;
        margin: 1rem auto 0 auto;
      }

      .banner-content {
        max-width: 100%;
      }
    }

    /* ===== Card Grid ===== */
    .card-grid {
      display: grid;
      grid-template-columns: repeat(4, 1fr);
      gap: 1.5rem;
      margin-top: 2rem;
    }

    @media (max-width: 1024px) {
      .card-grid {
        grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
      }
    }

    @media (max-width: 640px) {
      .card-grid {
        grid-template-columns: 1fr;
      }
    }

    .card {
      background: #fff;
      border: 1px solid #e5e7eb;
      border-radius: 16px;
      padding: 1.5rem;
      box-shadow: 0 4px 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.08);
      transition: transform 0.2s ease, box-shadow 0.2s ease;
      text-align: center;
    }

    .card:hover {
      transform: translateY(-4px);
      box-shadow: 0 8px 16px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.12);
    }

    .card h3 {
      margin-top: 0;
      font-size: 1.1rem;
      color: #111827;
    }

    .card p {
      font-size: 0.95rem;
      margin-top: 0.5rem;
    }

    /* ===== Let's Connect box ===== */
    .connect {
      margin-top: 3rem;
      background: #fff;
      border-radius: 12px;
      padding: 1.5rem;
      box-shadow: 0 4px 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.05);
    }

    .connect h2 {
      margin-top: 0;
      color: var(--kbm-green);
    }

    .connect a {
      color: var(--kbm-green);
      text-decoration: underline;
    }

    /* ===== Back to top button ===== */
    #kbm-top {
      position: fixed;
      bottom: 30px;
      right: 30px;
      width: 46px;
      height: 46px;
      border: none;
      border-radius: 50%;
      background: var(--kbm-green);
      color: #fff;
      font-size: 1.5rem;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      cursor: pointer;
      box-shadow: 0 4px 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.25);
      opacity: 0;
      visibility: hidden;
      transition: opacity 0.3s ease, visibility 0.3s ease, transform 0.2s ease;
      z-index: 9999;
    }

    #kbm-top.show {
      opacity: 1;
      visibility: visible;
    }

    #kbm-top:hover {
      background: var(--kbm-green-2);
      transform: translateY(-3px);
    }
  </style>

  <main>
    <div class="banner">
      <div class="banner-content">
        <div class="banner-title">Image or banner goes here</div>
        <p class="banner-note">
          This can be a headshot, a knitting machine setup, or a simple branded graphic.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="banner-photo">
        Photo<br />placeholder
      </div>
    </div>

    <h1>About Knit by Machine</h1>
    <div class="subhead">15 years helping knitters like you</div>

    <p>
      <strong>Knit by Machine</strong> is built on years of experience supporting knitters who want to feel confident with their machines.
    </p>

    <p>
      My goal is to take away the overwhelm and give you practical tools, resources, and encouragement so you can focus on creating projects you love.
    </p>

    <h2>My Story</h2>
    <p>
      I'm <strong>Sue Jalowiec</strong>, and for more than 15 years, I've been helping knitters overcome the challenges of machine knitting — from confusing instructions to projects that don't quite turn out as planned.
    </p>
    <p>
      That experience has shaped everything here at Knit by Machine, where the goal is simple: to give you the confidence and support you need to succeed with your machine.
    </p>
    <p>
      Knit by Machine is designed for knitters like you. It's a place where you'll find practical tools, clear resources, and encouraging guidance — all aimed at removing the guesswork so you can knit with confidence and actually enjoy the projects you start.
    </p>

    <h2>What You'll Discover</h2>
    <p>Here's a quick look at what you'll discover inside <strong>Knit by Machine</strong>:</p>

    <div class="card-grid">
      <div class="card">
        <h3>Patterns & Wizards</h3>
        <p>Custom-fit, step-by-step projects for any machine.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="card">
        <h3>Tutorials & Tips</h3>
        <p>Practical techniques explained clearly.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="card">
        <h3>Reference</h3>
        <p>Charts, tools, and guides all in one place.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="card">
        <h3>Support for All Levels</h3>
        <p>Confidence for beginners and inspiration for experienced knitters.</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <p style="margin-top:2rem;">
      Machine knitting doesn't have to feel overwhelming. With clear steps and the right tools, you can knit with confidence and enjoy the process.
      That's what Knit by Machine is here to give you — clarity, confidence, and encouragement.
    </p>

    <div class="connect">
      <h2>Let's Connect</h2>
      <p>
        If you'd like help, have a question, or just want to say hello, I'd love to hear from you.<br />
        Reach out anytime at <a href="mailto:contact@knitbymachine.com">contact@knitbymachine.com</a>.
      </p>
    </div>

    <button id="kbm-top" aria-label="Back to top">↑</button>
  </main>

  <script>
    const topBtn = document.getElementById("kbm-top");
    if (topBtn) {
      window.addEventListener("scroll", () => {
        if (window.scrollY > 200) topBtn.classList.add("show");
        else topBtn.classList.remove("show");
      });
      topBtn.addEventListener("click", () => {
        window.scrollTo({ top: 0, behavior: "smooth" });
      });
    }
  </script>
</Layout>
